txt.en: 'Easterling cat-masters train vicious battle-cats to do their bidding. They pose grave danger to us Rangers and forward scouts who go before the Host of the West.'
Easterling-trained battle-cats are a serious threat to scouts and Rangers who go before the Host of the West.
Cat-masters and battle-cats can be found in Lang Rhuven on the border of Dagorlad.\n\nYou should defeat cat-masters and battle-cats found in Lang Rhuven.
You have successfully defeated many of the cat-masters and battle-cats that add to the ferocity of the Khundolar empire.
Defeated many cat-masters and battle-cats in Lang Rhuven.
